        <ul>
          <li>New "Close Other Folders" menu item to help clean up your sidebar</li>
          <li>Save and restore cyclic search setting</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Other updates:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Add keyboard shortcuts to menu items</li>
